problem:
check whether the number is positive or negative or zero.

Source code:
#include <stdio.h>
int main() {
    int b;
    scanf("%d",&b);
    if(b<0)
    {
        printf("negative number");
    }
    else if(b>0)
    {
        printf("Positive number");
    }
    else 
    {
        printf("number is zero");
    }
}
